Package org.svvrl.goal.gui.menu

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutomatonPopupMenu
    An AutomatonPopupMenu is a popup menu for an automaton editor.
    HelpMenu
    This is a menu containing actions for help content.
    LayoutMenu
    This is a menu containing actions for laying out an automation.
    MenuFactory
    This object is used to initialize a menu bar or a menu.
    MenuFactory.ComponentDescriptor
    This is used to describe a menu or an action.
    MoveToMenu
    This is a menu containing actions for moving a tab to a window.
    RecentFileMenu
    This is a menu containing actions for opening recent files.
    UIMenu
    A UIMenu is a menu used in a window.
